
==== NAME ====

Posy::Plugin::ThisFlavour - Posy plugin to change local links to the current
flavour


==== VERSION ====

This describes version ``0.40'' of Posy::Plugin::ThisFlavour.


==== DESCRIPTION ====

This plugin changes local links in entries from the default flavour into the
current flavour (if the flavours are not the same).


==   Configuration   ==

This expects configuration settings in the $self->{config} hash, which, in
the default Posy setup, can be defined in the main "config" file in the data
directory.

``this_flavour_convert_links''
Set this_flavour_convert_links to off (zero) to turn off this plugin (for
example, to give different behaviour in different directories). (default:
on)


==== REQUIRES ====

    Posy
    Posy::Core

    Test::More


